			<div itemprop=3D"text">
			=09
					<div class=3D"bbWrapper">That's it!<br>
<br>
If I change my equipment profile so that my mash tun is 5 gallons in size (=
my needed mash volume), the infusion tool and the mash tab on my recipe bot=
h give 75.32 C.<br>
<br>
It's a weird way to make that calculation though isn't it? My mash tun is a=
 cooler with a lid so it's going to absorb the same amount of heat regardle=
ss of the size of my mash.</div>
